text: The Dolphins are a professional rugby league team from Redcliffe, a suburb of Brisbane. They compete in the National Rugby League (NRL). The Dolphins are the newest team in the NRL, only being created in 2021 and beginning their first season in 2023. They are the fourth NRL team in Queensland (after the Brisbane Broncos, the Gold Coast Titans and the North Queensland Cowboys) and the second team in Brisbane (after the Broncos). ==References== Category:2023 establishments in Australia Category:National Rugby League Category:Sports clubs and teams in Brisbane
